The Scoop

Save Time, Order Online

Simply place your order online, come to Cal Tort and your food will be waiting.

Burrito Elito Card

Don’t have one yet? Pick up a free card from a cashier, or download the app, and for every $1 you spend, you’ll get one point and when you reach 75 points you'll get $5 in Burrito Bucks! For more information, visit our Burrito Elito.

10% Military Discount

When you show your ID or come in uniform.

Monday Night Burrito Wheel

Come in on Mondays after 5pm, buy a regular sized burrito, and spin our world famous Burrito wheel You’re guaranteed to win something tasty.

Creative Catering

There isn't a party we can't handle. Call us today to cater your next event.

Mexican Food Menu

Our menu includes fresh burritos, burrito bowls, tacos, taco salads, fajitas, quesadillas, nachos and more.

The Scoop

Monday Night Burrito Wheel

Come in on Monday's after 5:00 pm, buy a regular sized burrito, and spin our World Famous Monday Night Wheel! You are guaranteed to win some delicious food.

Delivery Now Available

Order your California Tortilla favorites through our website to the surrounding Bethesda, MD area. Limited delivery zone available.

Burrito Elito Card

Don't have one yet? Pick one up, for free, at our store or download the app and for every $1 you spend you earn a point and when you hit 75 points you earn $5 in Burrito Bucks. Plus, you get a free burrito on your birthday!

Mexican Catering

We offer creative catering options for parties, corporate events and more. Have Cal Tort catering help you throw a Burrito Party, Fajita-Bar Party, Taco-Bar Party or order à la carte.

On the Menu

Our Mexican food menu features the best burritos, tacos, quesadillas, fajitas, salads and more.
